OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFriday,
OL,6,Fpatchy cloud and sunny intervals, very
OL,7,Fwarm, chance of showers. Cloudy
OL,8,FSaturday and Sunday, risk of rain or
OL,9,Fshowers at times. Cooler with
OL,10,Fgenerally light winds.
